com.bitplan.iri

Class IRIParserBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bitplan.iri.IRIParserBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRIParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class IRIParserBaseListener
extends Object
implements IRIParserListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of IRIParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
